==English==

===Etymology===
From ''Toxophilus'', the title of a 1535 book by [[w:Ascham|Ascham]] intended to mean ‘lover of the bow’, from Greek [[τοξον]] ‘bow’ + [[φίλος]].

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/tɒk'sɒfɪlʌɪt/}}

===Adjective===
{{en-ad|toxophilite}}

# pertaining to [[archery]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# an [[archer]]

[[vi:toxophilite]]